response.body:
# [4.11.0](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/compare/v4.10.1...v4.11.0) (2022-03-05)


### Bug Fixes

* `videoDetails.age_restricted` is always `false` in other languages ([#986](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/issues/986)) ([21bc728](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/commit/21bc728b5220a9f84f0626edca9675f286343390))
* trim id's passed to the url-utils ([#1073](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/issues/1073)) ([b35bdad](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/commit/b35bdad3be90e32d3f2c4546c01d69082d691962))


### Features

* add IPv6 block rotating ([#713](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/issues/713)) ([06f5611](https://github.com/fent/node-ytdl-core/commit/06f5611817a7a8acd41e2bc6284c979d9bd8e8cd))
